collections.name: GHIBALLERS
collections.description:
GHIBALLERS is an exclusive NFT collection that reimagines the world’s most legendary footballers in the enchanting art style of Studio Ghibli. Each piece captures the spirit, charisma, and passion of iconic players through a magical, nostalgic, and intricately detailed visual language.

Blending the beauty of anime with the universal love of football, GHIBALLERS offers a unique collectible experience for art lovers, football fans, and digital collectors alike. Every NFT is a tribute to greatness — on the pitch and in imagination.

collections.name: AI Prompt Cards
collections.description:
**AI Prompt Cards** are collectible digital cards inspired by the book *AI for Everyone: Crafting Prompts Without Coding Skills*. Each card captures a powerful prompt pattern, tip, or visual from the book—designed to help you think creatively and prompt more effectively.

Whether you're a reader, an AI enthusiast, or a curious creator, these cards give you:

- Bonus content and exclusive prompt templates  
- Visual inspiration to fuel your prompt journey  
- Access to future perks and community events  

Created in collaboration with Manifold, and viewable on [Manifold Studio](https://studio.manifold.xyz/contracts/209776880) and [OpenSea](https://opensea.io/collection/ai-prompt-cards).  

No crypto experience needed—just curiosity.

collections.name: Celestial Clash
collections.description:
The image depicts a powerful and dramatic battle between angelic and demonic forces, possibly inspired by religious or mythological themes. At the top, an angelic figure—likely Archangel Michael—wears white robes and golden armor, wielding a radiant sword. His large, majestic wings spread out as he leads other angels into battle. These angels, armed with swords and shields, appear to be descending from the heavens, their expressions and poses exuding determination and strength.

Below, monstrous demons with bat-like wings, red skin, and twisted horns rise from the fiery depths. Their snarling faces and aggressive postures suggest defiance and rage as they prepare to clash with the celestial warriors. The environment is engulfed in fire and darkness, contrasting with the bright heavenly light above. The entire composition is filled with action, movement, and tension, emphasizing the eternal struggle between good and evil.

collections.name: Legends of Freedom
collections.description:
Legends of Freedom: Madiba
This NFT pays tribute to the legendary Nelson Mandela, a symbol of resilience, peace, and justice. As an advocate for freedom and equality, Madiba's legacy continues to inspire millions around the world. Through this unique digital artwork, we celebrate the timeless spirit of one of the most influential figures in modern history.
Own a piece of history and the enduring power of Madiba’s legacy. This NFT is a homage to the fight for freedom and the hope that never fades.

collections.name: Faceless Memories
collections.description:
“Faceless Memories” is a collection of oil-on-canvas works capturing what cannot be named: the echo of what was lived, inherited, or felt. Figures without features, scenes frozen in time, gestures that speak without words. Each piece opens a crack into the unseen, the intimate, the persistent.

Created by Cuban artist Alid Nail, this series walks the line between remembrance and absence, inviting the viewer to fill in the silence with their own story.

collections.name: Divine Resonance: A Sacred Metallic Pantheon
collections.description:
Divine Resonance is a limited 1/1 NFT series honoring ancient archetypes through radiant digital paintings of Hindu and Buddhist deities—Garuda, Wishnu, Shiva, and Brahma—each depicted in luminous gold, silver, and copper tones. Fusing sacred symbolism with epic visual storytelling, each piece is rendered in ultra-high resolution, with no visible AI traces.

Every NFT includes unlockable content: a 30MB master file (.PNG/.PNP) for collectors to archive, display, or print. The collection channels elemental forces—Air, Water, Fire, Ether—through divine energy and sacred metallic geometry.

This is more than art—it’s a digital relic for those who resonate with power, myth, and balance. Hosted on Ethereum. Verified files via IPFS.

Created by CryptoMic, a visionary artist exploring the cosmic mirror within us all.

collections.name: tiled face
collections.description:
In a world that is increasingly shaped by digital identities, the NFT collection "tiled face" presents a reflection of our time. The starting point is the photo of a real person - a portrait that was transformed and further developed with the help of AI. Through the creative use of algorithms, unique digital artworks have been created that abstracts the original image and transfer it into new visual dimensions.

The pixelated faces symbolize the fusion of human and digital reality, the fragmentation of our identity in the connected world and the question of individuality in the age of artificial intelligence. Each NFT in this collection is a unique image of a human being - and at the same time a reflection of our digital existence.
